K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"0d6526af2ac749717999605a4f4caa4e625873fb","tid":1666893,"uid":306999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c5a4deea5f191825d3beac4b11cce7c3e211020","tid":1666893,"uid":14880,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"8ac20c08115a46fd70098a21d5a381c93ec6eebf","tid":1666893,"uid":306999,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"38e06039454ebd75812dafacc5b79e7c715f3c35","tid":1666893,"uid":14880,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:33:07.000Z","msg":"虹吸原理 用用完既生理鹽水樽仔唧哂裡面d空氣出黎 再放落水少少少少咁吸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"嘩！咁要玩好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"都話玩左幾個鐘 下次會帶粗針筒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"養魚換水果啲虹吸筒得唔得？"},{"pid":"c52a0b9f7b6e40f6630c3ee18055b0dea7d58e8b","tid":1666893,"uid":306999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d6526af2ac749717999605a4f4caa4e625873fb","tid":1666893,"uid":306999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c5a4deea5f191825d3beac4b11cce7c3e211020","tid":1666893,"uid":14880,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"8ac20c08115a46fd70098a21d5a381c93ec6eebf","tid":1666893,"uid":306999,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"嘩！咁要玩好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"都話玩左幾個鐘 下次會帶粗針筒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"養魚換水果啲虹吸筒得唔